$${\bar {\nu }_e\rightarrow \bar {\nu }_\mu }$$
\end{document} oscillations. These oscillations would result in the observation of muons produced via the charged current interaction of νμ’s and ν̄μ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
